name: Infiltrator (itch) (Mimo)
description:
The objective of the game is to get to the floating platform, there are infinite levels as they are  randomly generated. The controls can be found by going into the in-game settings along with a more in-depth description as how to play and what to do.

PS. This is my first attempt at a game. I used HTML, JS, CSS and p5.js libary.
